[{"section":"Work","slug":"/zh/work/unity-urp-decal-shader/","title":"Directional Decal Shader for Environmental Blending In Unity","description":"A directional decal shader that blends materials based on surface height and world orientation—ideal for effects like snow, sand, or dust accumulation.","date":"2024年12月12日","image":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/unity-urp-decal-shader/CathyShih_ProjectEris_DecalShader_Demo_hudbf9e5ada1e8bb3163280fc16ee96f3d_161679_420x0_resize_q80_h2_lanczos_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"420\"\n          height=\"279\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/unity-urp-decal-shader\\/CathyShih_ProjectEris_DecalShader_Demo_hudbf9e5ada1e8bb3163280fc16ee96f3d_161679_420x0_resize_lanczos_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","imageSM":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n          \n          \n          \n          \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/unity-urp-decal-shader/CathyShih_ProjectEris_DecalShader_Demo_hudbf9e5ada1e8bb3163280fc16ee96f3d_161679_100x100_fill_q80_h2_lanczos_smart1_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"100\"\n          height=\"100\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/unity-urp-decal-shader\\/CathyShih_ProjectEris_DecalShader_Demo_hudbf9e5ada1e8bb3163280fc16ee96f3d_161679_100x100_fill_lanczos_smart1_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","searchKeyword":"","categories":"Decal, Shader","tags":"decal, unity, shader, environment","content":"When working with assets in Unity projects, I often find that props can feel \u0026ldquo;out of place\u0026rdquo; in the environment. To address this, I created a custom decal shader that helps blend props more naturally into the scene.\nThis shader blends decals onto 3D models based on surface height and world orientation, similar to how snow or sand naturally accumulates on upward-facing surfaces.\nUnity 2022.3.16f1LTS URP 14.0.9 Shader Graph 14.0.9 It supports full material channel blending, including base color, normal map (bump), smoothness, metallic gloss, ambient occlusion and optional emission. Users can fine-tune the decal\u0026rsquo;s appearance with customizable parameters such as decal albedo texture, decal height and blend strength.\nFor convenience, the shader uses a packed decal mask texture (R = Metallic, G = Ambient Occlusion, B = Height, A = Smoothness), following the same format as the Mask Map used by Unity’s TerrainLit shader in HDRP and URP. This ensures consistency across assets and streamlines the workflow for developers already using Unity’s terrain systems.\n"},{"section":"Work","slug":"/zh/work/unity-urp-vertex-blend-triplanar-shader/","title":"Unity頂點混合紋理映射著色器(Vertex Blend Triplanar Shader)","description":"這個著色器(Shader)依據頂點的顏色混合多個紋理。","date":"2024年4月12日","image":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/unity-urp-vertex-blend-triplanar-shader/CathyShih_StylizedSandstoneCliff_Demo_hu5917f201cf00efb3a2d05493aa011cd2_1161027_420x0_resize_q80_h2_lanczos_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"420\"\n          height=\"354\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/unity-urp-vertex-blend-triplanar-shader\\/CathyShih_StylizedSandstoneCliff_Demo_hu5917f201cf00efb3a2d05493aa011cd2_1161027_420x0_resize_lanczos_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","imageSM":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n          \n          \n          \n          \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/unity-urp-vertex-blend-triplanar-shader/CathyShih_StylizedSandstoneCliff_Demo_hu5917f201cf00efb3a2d05493aa011cd2_1161027_100x100_fill_q80_h2_lanczos_smart1_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"100\"\n          height=\"100\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/unity-urp-vertex-blend-triplanar-shader\\/CathyShih_StylizedSandstoneCliff_Demo_hu5917f201cf00efb3a2d05493aa011cd2_1161027_100x100_fill_lanczos_smart1_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","searchKeyword":"","categories":"3D地形, 著色器(Shader)","tags":"3D地形, unity引擎, 著色器(Shader)","content":"我剛開始使用Unity時，對地形紋理混合的方式並不滿意。因此我開發了這個頂點混合紋理映射著色器(Vertex Blend Triplanar Shader)，讓我可以將Splat map貼圖烤到模型上來直接套用紋理。\n這個著色器運用三維模型頂點的顏色(Vertex colors)、以映射(Triplanar)的方式混合多個紋理。用這個方法替3D地形上色是因為一般的上色在高角度的地形紋理會被拉伸而不美觀，而運用映射的方式則能避免紋理拉伸。\n著色器運用可自定義的高度圖混合不同的紋理來實現真實的地形紋理 - 如上圖凸出的石頭與凹槽處堆積砂石間的紋理混合。對偏好使用三維模型創建地形的人來說非常適合。\nUnity 2022.3.16f1LTS URP 14.0.9 Shader Graph 14.0.9 著色器運用和Unity地形引擎相同的紋理遮罩通道，因此可直接套用適用於Unity地形引擎的紋理遮罩(Mask Textures)。\n目前這個著色器運用RGB通道來混合3個紋理。Alpha通道可以用來混合第4個紋理。\n展示的樣品是程式化生成的峭壁和紋理。Splat map貼圖自動依據模型的角度生成，並轉貼到頂點顏色。\n這裡是另一個運用此著色器的案例，你可以使用Unity引擎中的Polybrush來直接對頂點顏色進行更改或繪製，以達到滿意的效果。\n你可以到我的Github下載這個著色器。\n"},{"section":"Work","slug":"/zh/work/unity-urp-anisohighlight-hair-shader/","title":"Unity各向異頭髮高光著色器(Anisotropic Highlight Shader)","description":"運用各向異頭髮高光著色器(Anisotropic Highlight Shader)改善Unity通用渲染管線(URP)對頭髮高光渲染的視覺美感。","date":"2024年1月20日","image":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \u003cimg\n        src=\"/images/unity-urp-anisohighlight-hair-shader/CathyShih_MoveMainLightDemo.gif\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n        alt=\"\"\n        class=\" img\"\n        width=\"420\"\n        height=\"\" /\u003e\n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","imageSM":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \u003cimg\n        src=\"/images/unity-urp-anisohighlight-hair-shader/CathyShih_MoveMainLightDemo.gif\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n        alt=\"\"\n        class=\" img\"\n        width=\"100\"\n        height=\"100\" /\u003e\n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","searchKeyword":"","categories":"頭髮, 著色器(Shader)","tags":"頭髮, unity引擎, 著色器(Shader), UMA角色創建","content":"下圖左: Unity通用渲染管線預設Lit著色器; 中: UMA角色創建建議使用的SpeedTree8著色器; 右: 我的著色器 頭髮模型在遊戲中很常用，但是Unity預設的URP材質對於頭髮著色並沒有達到我想要的效果。因此，我開發了這個各向異性高光頭髮著色器來增強專案中的頭髮渲染。\n這個著色器(Shader)的目的是改善Unity通用渲染管線(URP)對頭髮高光渲染的視覺美感。\nUnity 2022.3.16f1LTS URP 14.0.9 Shader Graph 14.0.9 這個著色器(Shader)運用了Unity專案 BoatAttack 中的主光著色器來獲取主光的方向和顏色。使用這個著色器需要附上各向異方向材質。以下的渲染結果使用了WillB的UMA(Unity Multipurpose Avatar System)頭髮模型。當光的方向改變時的渲染結果:\n運用的模型紋理(Texture):\nUMA是一個免費的角色創建系統，UMA的使用者經常會需要改變頭髮材質的顏色，以下是改變顏色後的效果:\n你可以到我的Github下載這個著色器。\n"},{"section":"Work","slug":"/zh/work/80s-hair-model/","title":"80年代髮型在Unity中渲染","description":"80年代髮型在UnityURP中渲染，我使用Blender製作了80年代髮型，採用了通常與ZBrush相關的常見頭髮創建工作流程。","date":"2023年12月20日","image":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/80s-hair-model/CathyShih_80sHairModel_2_hueaaf4ee0dc43a347f581cd22b4ec8ec0_1115718_420x0_resize_q80_h2_lanczos_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"420\"\n          height=\"525\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/80s-hair-model\\/CathyShih_80sHairModel_2_hueaaf4ee0dc43a347f581cd22b4ec8ec0_1115718_420x0_resize_lanczos_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","imageSM":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n          \n          \n          \n          \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/80s-hair-model/CathyShih_80sHairModel_2_hueaaf4ee0dc43a347f581cd22b4ec8ec0_1115718_100x100_fill_q80_h2_lanczos_smart1_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"100\"\n          height=\"100\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/80s-hair-model\\/CathyShih_80sHairModel_2_hueaaf4ee0dc43a347f581cd22b4ec8ec0_1115718_100x100_fill_lanczos_smart1_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","searchKeyword":"","categories":"頭髮","tags":"頭髮, unity引擎, 著色器(Shader), Blender(3D繪圖)","content":"\r我使用 Blender 製作了 80 年代的髮型，並採用了通常與ZBrush相關的常見頭髮創建工作流程。該過程涉及雕刻頭髮形狀並放置髮卡曲線以進行分層-從基礎層到分離層再到過渡層。\n髮卡的創建完全在Blender中完成，利用其頭髮工具、幾何節點(Geometry Nodes)和著色器(Shader Nodes)。 最終渲染是使用URP中的Unity著色器(Shadergraph)創建的各向異性高光頭髮著色器完成的。\n此模型由大約35k個三角形組成。此圖像直接從 Unity 截圖，沒有任何額外的編輯或後製。\n"},{"section":"Work","slug":"/zh/work/traditional-art/","title":"傳統藝術作品","description":"我的傳統藝術作品。","date":"2020年12月20日","image":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/traditional-art/CathyShih_TraditionalArtwork-thumbnail_hu50aafda09112da919ba980eff0636cda_4089613_420x0_resize_q80_h2_lanczos_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"420\"\n          height=\"232\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/traditional-art\\/CathyShih_TraditionalArtwork-thumbnail_hu50aafda09112da919ba980eff0636cda_4089613_420x0_resize_lanczos_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","imageSM":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n    \n      \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n    \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n          \n          \n          \n          \n        \n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n        \u003cimg\n          \n            src=\"/images/traditional-art/CathyShih_TraditionalArtwork-thumbnail_hu50aafda09112da919ba980eff0636cda_4089613_100x100_fill_q80_h2_lanczos_smart1_3.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"\n          \n\n          alt=\"\"\n          class=\"  img\"\n          width=\"100\"\n          height=\"100\"\n          onerror=\"this.onerror='null';this.src='\\/images\\/traditional-art\\/CathyShih_TraditionalArtwork-thumbnail_hu50aafda09112da919ba980eff0636cda_4089613_100x100_fill_lanczos_smart1_3.png';\" /\u003e\n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n  \n\n\n  \n","searchKeyword":"","categories":"傳統藝術","tags":"傳統藝術, 炭筆素描, 水彩, 粉彩筆, 水墨畫","content":"\r我的傳統藝術作品。\n"}]